values: last night i drove to elk grove at 3am and picked up 2 white motorolas(mdma)and ate one of them. by far the best drug experience ive had in a long fucking time. me and buddy journeyed around the track for an hour or so. i still have one pill left but im going to keep it in reserve! jay got his GED, im fucking proud of him hes really turned things around, im supposed to meet up with him later tonight. me and dave went to ocb yesterday and ate until we couldnt eat no more. o and in other news me and nikki are gonna be friends for now and if something more happens it will happen. im really happy with where our relationship is now. we fgucked around for a while and had fun but she is seriously an awesome friend and i dont want to screw that up. anyways im done for now!

it was weird being outside and actually watching the rain turn to snow. tensions were high today at work, andria said she was about to cry because things were getting so hectic and crazy.i got out a half an hour late and then met up with jp. we played guitar and keyboard at his apartment for an hour or so. so i asked nikki out on a date last night. thats right A DATE, usually id just say do you wanna hang out but i threw in the word just to see what she would say. she was extremely happy which is weird considering we hang out all the time. i guess she is just happy im trying to go to the next level with her. or something like that. my older bro brought home hot wings from hooters. FUCK THAT. i ate two and now my mouth is hotter than the inside of john goodmans ass!!.......uh, yeah ill close with that. -peace
